A full fort will work... assuming nothing picks up the boulders, you
have a suitable ranged attack to zap at the troll, and the troll doesn't
revive during the turns it will take you to open the fort and get to his
corpse.

A single boulder will just get you zapped when the troll goes around the
boulder to get to you, unless you can guarantee the troll stays in a
corridor; but this magnifies the problem of &quot;how do I get to the wand
before the troll revives?&quot;

Better choice than the fort: dig for the wand and wish up MR/Reflection.

--
Derek

