CM is another slight danger, but having an escape route open and being
reasonably healthy should suffice. 22 times in 23, only one
(level-appropriate) monster will be summoned, which shouldn't be a problem
at all. In the other cases, E-word and running away should save you. Doing
it in a corridor might even be a bad idea, since monsters will be summoned
on both sides, obstructing your escape.

